  "title": "🤗WELCOME FRESH GRADS🤗 Sales & Marketing- office hours/traveling opportunities",
  "description": "<p><strong>Hey Hey! Are you seeking an opportunity that helps you improve and grow your personality?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Our company is expanding!!</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are looking for an enthusiastic Junior Marketing to join our growing team. We provide development on personal growth, communication skills and we never fail to see teammates walking in and out of the office smiling. :)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>-Achieve sales target and improve the sales of clients' company</p>\n<p>-Creating awareness about the product or services that our clients is providing</p>\n<p>-Lead a sales and marketing team and facilitating team’s growth</p>\n<p>-Get involved in client’s marketing through business development</p>\n<p>-Develop analytical and problem-solving skills</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What do we want from you?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>-No experience? Fear not, personal mentorship and guidance are provided!</strong></p>\n<p>-Keen learning attitude and enjoy interacting with new people</p>\n<p>-Hunger for personal development and progress</p>\n<p>-Team player</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p>-Attractive Performance Incentives</p>\n<p><strong>-Overseas Travelling Opportunities</strong></p>\n<p>-Fun Environment</p>\n<p>-Team bonding activities</p>\n<p><strong>Summary of role requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>No experience required for this role</li>\n  <li>Working rights required for this role</li>\n  <li>No experience required for this role</li>\n  <li>Expected salary: $3000-$5000 per month</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>\n<p>Join us today!</p>",
